description: RARELY AVAILABLE EAST SIDE TOWNHOME WITH 2 DEEDED PARKING SPOTS AND ROOF DECK!  DRAMATIC FLOOR PLAN OFFERS TWO STORY LIVING AREA WITH CUSTOM METROPOLITAN CABINETS, STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES, QUARTZ COUNTERS AND FARMERS SINK.  DESIGNATED DINING AREA, LIVING ROOM WITH SOARING CEILINGS, GAS FIREPLACE AND OVERSIZED WINDOWS WITH CUSTOM WINDOW TREATMENTS. TWO KING SIZE MASTER SUITES, FAMILY ROOM, ROOF DECK WITH DIRECT WATER VIEWS, PATIO AND GREEN SPACE.  ADDITIONAL FEATURES INCLUDE HARDWOOD FLOORS, LAUNDRY, CENTRAL AIR AND TWO PARKING SPOTS INCLUDING 1 GARAGE AND 1 OUTSIDE.  THIS FRONT FACING NANTUCKET STYLE HOME IS LOCATED IN SOUTH BOSTONS MOST SOUGHT AFTER WATERFRONT LOCATION.
